### ================== RUTAS SIN AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todas las vacunas (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/public

### Obtener vacuna por ID (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/public/1

### Crear una nueva vacuna (SIN token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vacuna Antirrábica",
  "description": "Vacuna para prevenir la rabia",
  "manufacturer": "Pfizer",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar una vacuna (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/public/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vacuna Antirrábica Actualizada",
  "description": "Vacuna actualizada para prevención de rabia",
  "manufacturer": "Moderna",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar una vacuna físicamente (SIN token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/public/1

### Desactivar una vacuna (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/public/2/deactivate

### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todas las vacunas (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener vacuna por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear una nueva vacuna (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vacuna Triple Viral",
  "description": "Vacuna contra sarampión, rubéola y paperas",
  "manufacturer": "GSK",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar una vacuna (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vacuna Triple Viral Actualizada",
  "description": "Vacuna actualizada contra sarampión, rubéola y paperas",
  "manufacturer": "GSK Updated",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar una vacuna físicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Desactivar una vacuna (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/vaccines/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
